tasks.title: Analyze market trends for AI automation
tasks.description: Research and identify emerging trends in AI-powered automation tools

tasks.title: Design an AI-powered workflow automation system
tasks.description: Create a system that can learn from human workflows and automate repetitive tasks

tasks.title: Design an AI-powered workflow automation system
tasks.description: Create a system that can learn from human workflows and automate repetitive tasks

tasks.title: Design an AI-powered recommendation system
tasks.description: Create an intelligent recommendation engine that learns user preferences and suggests personalized content. Should handle cold start problem and scale to millions of users.

tasks.title: Build an intelligent chatbot that learns from conversations
tasks.description: Design and implement a conversational AI system that improves over time by learning from user interactions. Must handle context, remember previous conversations, and provide personalized responses.

tasks.title: Design an AI system that can predict user needs before they ask
tasks.description: Create an intelligent predictive system that analyzes user behavior patterns, learns preferences over time, and proactively suggests solutions. Should handle millions of users with real-time predictions.

tasks.title: Create a voice-controlled smart home system with natural language understanding
tasks.description: Design and build a voice AI that understands context, learns user preferences, and controls all smart home devices intelligently. Should handle Indian English accents and multiple languages.

tasks.title: Build a multilingual AI chatbot for Indian languages
tasks.description: Create an intelligent chatbot that understands Hindi, English, Tamil, Telugu, Bengali and other Indian languages. Should handle code-mixing and regional dialects naturally.

discussions.topic: How can we automate complex business processes using AI?
